</div>
<!-- About Section -->
<div id="about">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row" id="quota">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
                <div class="Quota">
                    <h2>Send a quota</h2> 

                    <div id="alert" class="error-dialog hide-item">
                        <div class="msg">
                            Something went Wrong 
                        </div>
                    </div>
    @using (Html.BeginForm("sendQuota", "home"))
    {
        @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
        @Html.ValidationSummary()
        <div class="form-group">

            @Html.LabelFor(m => m.quota.Email, new { @class = "control-label" })
            @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.quota.Email, new { @class = "form-control", id = "email", placeholder = "Enter your email address" })
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">

            @Html.LabelFor(m => m.quota.Source, new { @class = "control-label" })
            @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.quota.Source, new { @class = "form-control", id="source" ,placeholder = "Where is the package coming from" })
        </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        @Html.LabelFor(m => m.quota.Destination, new { @class = "control-label" })
                        @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.quota.Destination, new { @class = "form-control", id="des", placeholder = "Destination of the package" })
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        @Html.LabelFor(m => m.quota.packageInfo, new { @class = "control-label" })
                        @Html.TextAreaFor(m => m.quota.packageInfo, new { @class = "form-control", placeholder = "Detail information of the package" })
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <button class="btn btn-site btn-lg">Send</button>

                    </div>
    }
                        </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
                    <p>
                        ShpimentPRO is a leading logistics and distribution services company established in 2005. We offer a wide array of express courier and logistic support solutions to our various customers.

                        With over 400 highly skilled personnel, we have excellent competencies in striving sectors such as Financial Services, Manufacturing, Telecommunications, Government Agencies, and Oil & Gas/Utilities. As a diverse end-to-end logistics solutions provider, we offer a range of expertise aimed at helping customers re-engineer and re-invent their businesses to compete successfully in an ever-changing marketplace, with the final objective of safely and promptly delivering all our customers consignments as expected.
                    </p>
                    <h3>Why Choose Us?</h3>
                    <div class="list-style">
                        <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                            <ul>
                                <li>Years of Experience</li>
                                <li>Fully Insured</li>
                                <li>Cost Control Experts</li>
                                <li>100% Satisfaction Guarantee</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                            <ul>
                                <li>Free Consultation</li>
                                <li>Satisfied Customers</li>
                                <li>Accountability</li>
                                <li>Execution</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- Services Section -->
<div id="services">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-media"> <img src="~/courierImages/International.jpg" alt=" "> </div>
                <div class="service-desc">
                    <h3>
                        International Service
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Express delivery of time sensitive documents and parcels globally. Time in transit is usually between 24 to 72 hours. Consignments up to 500kg. Optional insurance for all types of shipments.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-media"> <img src="~/courierImages/custom.jpg" alt=" "> </div>
                <div class="service-desc">
                    <h3>Custom  business Service</h3>
                    <p>
                        Every business has different supply chain challenges; which means that standard solutions are rarely effective.
                        Our experience in creating “complete” logistics systems gives us considerable flexibility in how we work with you. Whether we focus on your entire supply chain or smaller elements within it, we can add measurable efficiency and cost savings to your business processes.
                        We’ll address material supply, ..
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="service-media"> <img src="~/courierImages/manDeliveringPackage.jpeg" alt=" "> </div>
                <div class="service-desc">
                    <h3>Door to Door Service</h3>
                    <p>
                        We offer the ultimate convenience for parcel deliveries. You can wave goodbye to hanging around at the post office thanks to our convenient door to door collection and delivery service. You can arrange everything from the comfort of your own home. Once you’ve booked, we’ll send you some shipping labels to print and attach to your parcel. Then, you can simply sit back and relax as we take care of the rest. We’ll collect your parcel straight from your front door and deliver it straight to where it needs to go. It really is that easy!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
       
    </div>
</div>

